This software is an out-of-tree LLVM pass plugin. It uses LLVM's header APIs at
build time. LLVM is a separate project, licensed under the Apache License 2.0
with LLVM exceptions (https://llvm.org/LICENSE.txt), and is not distributed with
this software.

Irreducible-loop detection uses LLVM's GenericCycleInfo, which implements the
single-pass DFS loop-identification algorithm of Wei, Tan, and Chen (SAS 2007).
